trans-unit.source: Defines a contract that components can use to access an object across application domain and process boundaries.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en kontrakt komponenter kan bruke til å få tilgang til et objekt på tvers av programmet domenet og behandle grenser.

trans-unit.source: When you implement IRemoteObjectContract on a type, components can use the contract to access type information for objects of the type.
trans-unit.target: Når du implementerer IRemoteObjectContract for en type, kan komponenter bruker kontrakten til å få tilgang til typeinformasjonen for objekter av typen.

trans-unit.source: Components access type information by calling the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A> method to obtain an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.
trans-unit.target: Komponenter tilgang til informasjon om ved å kalle <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>metoden for å hente en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> interface defines a contract that components can use to access specific type and member information, and to invoke members.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>grensesnittet definerer en kontrakt komponenter kan bruke tilgang til angitt type og medlemmet informasjon og aktivere medlemmer.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract"></xref> that specifies the type of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract"> </xref> som angir hvilken type gjeldende <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the GetRemoteType method to access the members of the remote object that the current <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract> identifies.
trans-unit.target: Bruk GetRemoteType-metoden til å få tilgang til medlemmer av eksterne objekt som gjeldende <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>identifiserer.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract"></xref> that specifies the type of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract"> </xref> som angir hvilken type gjeldende <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Casts the object identified by the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"></xref> to a specified type.
trans-unit.target: Kaster objektet som er angitt av gjeldende <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract"> </xref> til en angitt type.

trans-unit.source: The canonical name of the type to cast the object to.
trans-unit.target: Kanoniske navnet av type for å endre objektet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> that represents the result of the cast operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"> </xref> som representerer resultatet av endre-operasjonen.
